================================================================================
NOTICE: This repository is glue code only. It downloads and orchestrates
the following third-party projects, which retain their own copyrights and
licenses:

  - Thorium Web  (edrlab/thorium-web)  — BSD-3-Clause
  - Readium CLI  (readium/cli)         — BSD-3-Clause

When you run setup.ps1, those projects are fetched into ./thorium-web/ and
./tools/readium/ respectively. Their full LICENSE files travel with them and
must be retained.

The sample publication bundled in ./books/accessible_epub_3.epub originates
from the IDPF/epub3-samples project and is provided here for testing purposes
only, under the terms granted by its publishers.
